Patch Set 3:

Nikhil, thanks for raising these questions. I agree with you on ApiImpact flag, I can add this and I will.

However, I'm not sure that this patch should include documentation. I think that this is a bigger issue and it should be resolved by another change set.

As I understand whole metadata definitions API should be described here: http://developer.openstack.org/api-ref.html
The problem is that there is no documentation at all for this API (Am I wrong? Maybe I can't find correct link...). 

I'm also aware of this doc: http://docs.openstack.org/developer/glance/glancemetadefcatalogapi.html but it does not describe parameters that each property/object can take.

Any thoughts?
